          "id": "difficult-questions",
          "title": "Difficult Questions in Theology",
          "titleBgColor": "bg-green-500",
          "description": "Are all religions the same? Is God a construction? Are there any certainties? Here is a collection of L'Abri lectures on the most difficult questions of the day.",
          "backgroundImage": "/images/playlists/difficult-questions-bg.avif",
          "tracks": [
            { "displayTitle": "Is God Angry", "filename": "Are We Better Than God^ part 3_ Is God Angry^ - Wade Bradshaw___130.mp3" },
